<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Cookie Policy - AI Digital Friend</title>

  <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
  <%= csp_meta_tag %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
  <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    @keyframes waveAnimation {
      0% { transform: translateX(-100%) translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateX(0%) translateY(-20px); }
      100% { transform: translateX(100%) translateY(0px); }
    }

    @keyframes fogDrift {
      0% { transform: translateX(-50px) translateY(0px) scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }
      33% { transform: translateX(50px) translateY(-30px) scale(1.2); opacity: 0.6; }
      66% { transform: translateX(-30px) translateY(-10px) scale(0.9); opacity: 0.4; }
      100% { transform: translateX(-50px) translateY(0px) scale(1); opacity: 0.3; }
    }

    @keyframes crystallize {
      0% { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1); }
      50% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.8), 0 0 40px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5), 0 0 60px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3); }
      100% { text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5), 0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1); }
    }

    @keyframes waterRipple {
      0% { transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0px); }
      50% { transform: scale(1.05); filter: blur(1px); }
      100% { transform: scale(1); filter: blur(0px); }
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(75, 0, 130, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 40% 80%, rgba(25, 25, 112, 0.5) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 60% 20%, rgba(72, 61, 139, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%),
        linear-gradient(135deg, #000428 0%, #004e92 25%, #000000 50%, #434343 75%, #000000 100%);
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      min-height: 100vh;
      line-height: 1.6;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      position: relative;
    }

    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 60%, rgba(0, 255, 128, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%);
      animation: fogDrift 8s ease-in-out infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    body::after {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 300%;
      height: 100%;
      background: 
        repeating-linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          transparent,
          transparent 100px,
          rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.03) 100px,
          rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.03) 200px
        );
      animation: waveAnimation 15s linear infinite;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .hero-section {
      background: 
        radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 70%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 30%, rgba(138, 43, 226, 0.2) 0%, transparent 60%),
        radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 70%, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px) saturate(180%);
      padding: 6rem 2rem 4rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
      border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .hero-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3) 100%);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .hero-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: crystallize 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6));
    }

    .hero-title {
      font-size: 4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00ffff, #ff00ff, #00ff88, #ffff00, #00ffff);
      background-size: 300% 300%;
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      animation: crystallize 3s ease-in-out infinite, waveAnimation 6s ease-in-out infinite;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 20px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6),
        0 0 40px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.4),
        0 0 60px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2),
        0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.5));
    }

    .hero-tagline {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 300;
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
      opacity: 0.9;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
        0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      animation: waterRipple 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .content-section {
      background: 
        radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 50%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 70% 80%, rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 50%),
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.85);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 3rem;
      margin: 3rem 0;
      box-shadow: 
        0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7),
        inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1),
        0 0 50px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.1);
      backdrop-filter: blur(15px) saturate(150%);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2);
      position: relative;
      z-index: 5;
      animation: waterRipple 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .content-section::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -2px;
      left: -2px;
      right: -2px;
      bottom: -2px;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, 
        rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3), 
        rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.3), 
        rgba(0, 255, 128, 0.3), 
        rgba(255, 255, 0, 0.3));
      border-radius: 22px;
      z-index: -1;
      filter: blur(3px);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }

    h1 {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6);
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6),
        0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3),
        0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      animation: crystallize 4s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    h2 {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      border-bottom: 3px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6);
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 15px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.6),
        0 0 30px rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3),
        0 3px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      animation: crystallize 4s ease-in-out infinite;
      background: linear-gradient(45deg, #00ffff, #ffffff, #00ff88);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }

    h3 {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin: 2rem 0 1.5rem 0;
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4),
        0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
      animation: waterRipple 5s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    p {
      line-height: 1.8;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2),
        0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
      animation: waterRipple 7s ease-in-out infinite;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }

    ul {
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-left: 2rem;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      text-shadow: 
        0 0 5px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3),
        0 1px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
    }

    .highlight {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.2), rgba(255, 0, 255, 0.2));
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.3);
      animation: waterRipple 8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .friendly-message {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 128, 0.15), rgba(0, 255, 255, 0.15));
      border-radius: 15px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 255, 128, 0.3);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .emoji-large {
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      display: block;
      animation: crystallize 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    strong {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }
      
      .hero-tagline {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
      }
      
      .content-section {
        padding: 2rem;
        margin: 2rem 0;
      }
      
      h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }
      
      h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
      
      .container {
        padding: 1rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <section class="hero-section">
    <div class="hero-icon">üç™</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Cookie Policy</h1>
    <p class="hero-tagline">Simple, transparent, and cookie-free</p>
  </section>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-section">
      <div class="friendly-message">
        <span class="emoji-large">üéâ</span>
        <h2>Great News! We Don't Use Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>AI Digital Friend</strong> is designed with your privacy in mind. We're proud to say that our platform operates completely <strong>cookie-free</strong>!
        </p>
      </div>

      <h2>üåü What This Means for You</h2>
      <p>
        Unlike most websites that track your every move with cookies, we've built <strong>AI Digital Friend</strong> to respect your privacy from the ground up. Here's what makes us different:
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <h3>‚ú® No Tracking Cookies</h3>
        <p>We don't place any tracking cookies on your device. Your browsing habits and personal data stay private.</p>
        
        <h3>üîí No Marketing Cookies</h3>
        <p>We don't use cookies to build advertising profiles or share your data with third-party marketers.</p>
        
        <h3>üìä No Analytics Cookies</h3>
        <p>We don't use cookies to track your usage patterns or create detailed user profiles.</p>
        
        <h3>üö´ No Third-Party Cookies</h3>
        <p>We don't allow external services to place cookies through our platform.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>ü§ñ How We Provide Personalized AI Without Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        You might wonder: "How can AI Digital Friend remember my preferences and provide personalized experiences without cookies?" Great question! Here's our approach:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Account-Based Memory:</strong> When you create an account, your AI preferences are securely stored with your profile, not in cookies</li>
        <li><strong>Session Storage:</strong> We use temporary browser session storage that automatically clears when you close your browser</li>
        <li><strong>Local Processing:</strong> Many personalization features happen directly in your browser without sending data to our servers</li>
        <li><strong>Explicit Consent:</strong> Any data we store is with your explicit permission and can be deleted anytime</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>üõ°Ô∏è Essential Technical Functions</h2>
      <p>
        The only data we temporarily store in your browser is essential for the platform to function:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Authentication Tokens:</strong> To keep you securely logged in during your session</li>
        <li><strong>Security Measures:</strong> To protect against unauthorized access and ensure platform security</li>
        <li><strong>User Interface Preferences:</strong> To remember your theme preferences during your current session</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        <strong>Important:</strong> These are not "cookies" in the traditional sense - they're temporary session data that expires when you close your browser.
      </p>

      <h2>üåç Why We Chose to Go Cookie-Free</h2>
      <p>
        At <strong>Grand Pa United‚Ñ¢</strong>, we believe that powerful AI should come with powerful privacy protections. Our cookie-free approach reflects our core values:
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <h3>üéØ Privacy by Design</h3>
        <p>We built AI Digital Friend from the ground up with privacy as a fundamental feature, not an afterthought.</p>
        
        <h3>ü§ù Trust Through Transparency</h3>
        <p>We believe in being completely transparent about how we handle your data - and how we don't handle it.</p>
        
        <h3>üöÄ Innovation Without Compromise</h3>
        <p>We prove that cutting-edge AI experiences don't require sacrificing user privacy.</p>
      </div>

      <h2>üì± What About Third-Party Services?</h2>
      <p>
        While <strong>AI Digital Friend</strong> doesn't use cookies, some integrated services might have their own policies:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Payment Processors:</strong> When you make payments, secure payment providers may use their own session management</li>
        <li><strong>AI Model Providers:</strong> Our AI partners (like OpenAI) have their own privacy policies for API interactions</li>
        <li><strong>Security Services:</strong> Anti-fraud and security services may use temporary identifiers for protection</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
        We carefully vet all our partners to ensure they meet our high privacy standards.
      </p>

      <h2>‚öôÔ∏è Your Control Options</h2>
      <p>
        Even though we don't use cookies, you still have complete control:
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> You can configure your browser to block all cookies if you prefer</li>
        <li><strong>Account Settings:</strong> Manage all your data preferences directly in your AI Digital Friend account</li>
        <li><strong>Data Export:</strong> Download all your data anytime you want</li>
        <li><strong>Account Deletion:</strong> Permanently delete your account and all associated data</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="friendly-message">
        <span class="emoji-large">üíé</span>
        <h3>The Bottom Line</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>AI Digital Friend</strong> is committed to providing you with an amazing AI companion experience while keeping your privacy crystal clear. No cookies, no tracking, no hidden agendas - just powerful AI that respects your digital autonomy.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Questions?</strong> Contact our privacy team at <strong>privacy@aidigitalfriend.com</strong>
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight">
        <p>
          <strong>Last Updated:</strong> August 18, 2025<br>
          <strong>Effective Date:</strong> August 18, 2025<br>
          <strong>Next Review:</strong> February 18, 2026
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
